-> This is write down what you want to deploy as human readable formats
   no more clicks

-> Enables DevOps
  - it can be tracked in a version control system
  - enables better visibility and team collaboration

-> Declarative infrastructure

********* WORKFLOW **********

- WRITE
  - Setup a GITHUB repo to host your terraform codes for team to collaborate

- PLAN
  - This will reveal the changes the code will make to your infrastructure
  - you aLWAYS go back and forth between write and plan to perfect your code

- APPLY
  - you deploy the real infrastructure  
